JSON - JavaScript Object Notation
AJAX - Asyncrhonous JavaScript And XML

media type = application/json
extension = .json

tools
--------
https://jsonlint.com/ - JSON validator

fundamentals - JSON
----------------------
1. Always starts and ends with curly brackets {}
2. name should be quoted("") in name/value

Data Types - JSON
-------------------
1.Number 
2.String (with quote)
3.Boolean 
4.Array
5.Object
6.null

AJAX - fundamentals
--------------------
No refresh & can request,receive,send Data to a Server
not a programming language - combination of technology within the browser XHR object + JavaScript to connect the request data and the Document Object Model(DOM)

